
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <% include head %>

  <body class="text-center">

    <div class="cover-container d-flex h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
      <header class="masthead mb-auto">
        <div class="inner">
          <h3 class="masthead-brand"><img src="/images/bp.jpg" height="75"></h3>
          <nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-center">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
            <a class="nav-link active" href="about">About</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="contact">Contact</a>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main role="main" class="inner cover">
        <!-- <p class="lead"><img src="/images/watercolor.png" height="105"></p> -->
        <% if (email) { %>
          <h1 class="lead">Welcome, <%= email %>.</h1>
        <% } else { %>
          <h1 class="lead">Who Are We?</h1>
        <% } %>
        <p class="lead">In January 2021, four Chinese American college students came together to build Bridging Pacific -
          a nonprofit that provides organization that provides resources and communities for Chinese American immigrants.
          As immigrants’ daughters and sons, we are passionate about establishing a resource bank for Chinese immigrants to navigate the challenges of living in a new country.
          We are also building a community for the Chinese diaspora to connect and network. Join us in our journey!</p>
        <div class="lead">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm">
              <img src="/images/valentina.jpeg" class="rounded-circle" height="105">
              <div class="name">Valentina Xu</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm">
              <img src="/images/sharon.jpeg" class="rounded-circle" height="105">
              <div class="name">Sharon Chen</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm">
              <img src="/images/brandon.jpeg" class="rounded-circle" height="105">
              <div class="name">Brandon Shi</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm">
              <img src="/images/henry.jpeg" class="rounded-circle" height="105">
              <div class="name">Henry Lei</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="lead">Bridging Pacific 是由四位康奈尔和斯沃斯莫尔大学生创立的非盈利组织，致力于为中国移民家庭及留学生提供各种适应美国的资源和交流的平台。</p>
      </main>
      <% include foot %>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>
